com.airg.android.device

Class PreferenceStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.airg.android.device.PreferenceStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.SharedPreferences

    public class PreferenceStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.content.SharedPreferences
    A SharedPreferences implementation with a few extra features. This class wraps an Android native SharedPreferences instance for maximum compatibility.

      • PreferenceStore

        public PreferenceStore(android.content.Context context,
                       java.lang.String name)
        Create/access a non-default SharedPreferences store. This method wraps the Context.getSharedPreferences(String, int) with mode set to Context.MODE_PRIVATE.
        Parameters:
        context - context to access system paths
        name - preferences store file name

        Parameters:
        context - context to access system paths
        name - preferences store file name
        mode - preference store access mode (e.g. Context.MODE_PRIVATE
